HEADWORD: Uniterable
<hw>U*nit"er*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not iterable;
incapable of being repeated.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧To play
